---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppButton from '../components/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---


<Layout>
    <head>
    <meta name="description" content="Conoce al equipo de STOP CAE: abogados especialistas en defensa de deudores CAE, misión, visión y valores." />
</head>
    <Header />
    
    <main class="quienes-somos-page">
        <section class="quienes-somos-section">
            <div class="banner-container">
                <div class="banner-illustration">
                    <!-- Aquí puedes agregar una imagen o ilustración -->
                    <div class="illustration-placeholder">
    <img src="/assets/quienes-somos.webp" alt="Stop Excepción" class="banner-img" />
                            <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="#E0DCDC" stroke="#CA0101" stroke-width="2"/>
                            <path d="M70 90 L90 110 L130 70" stroke="#CA0101" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="banner-content">
                    <h1 class="banner-title">¡Defendemos tus derechos y te acompañamos en todo momento!</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

                        <style>

.banner-img {
  filter: invert(1) brightness(2) grayscale(1);

  size:auto;
}
</style>

        
                 <!-- Sección de Misión y Visión -->
         <section class="mission-vision-section">
             <div class="container">
                 <div class="mission-vision-grid">
                     <div class="mission-card">
                         <div class="card-icon">
                             <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
                         </div>
                         <h3>Misión</h3>
                         <p>Brindar asesoría y representación legal especializada a quienes han accedido a la educación superior, con el objetivo de eliminar sus deudas estudiantiles mediante procesos judiciales justos y efectivos. Trabajamos con compromiso, empatía y excelencia para que cada profesional pueda comenzar su vida laboral con libertad financiera y dignidad.</p>
                     </div>
                     <div class="vision-card">
                         <div class="card-icon">
                             <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                         </div>
                         <h3>Visión</h3>
                         <p>Ser el estudio jurídico líder en la eliminación de deudas estudiantiles, brindando a los profesionales la oportunidad de comenzar su vida laboral sin cargas injustas, reconociendo su esfuerzo, dedicación y compromiso con la educación como base de un futuro más justo y equitativo.</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
             </div>
         </section>
         
         <!-- Sección de Descripción Detallada -->
         <section class="detailed-description-section">
             <div class="container">
                 <h2 class="section-title">Nuestro Compromiso</h2>
                 <div class="description-cards-grid">
                     <div class="description-card">
                         <div class="card-header">
                             <div class="card-icon">
                                 <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                             </div>
                             <h3>Especialización Legal</h3>
                         </div>
                         <p>Somos un <span class="keyword">estudio jurídico especializado</span> en la <span class="keyword">eliminación de deudas estudiantiles</span> a través de <span class="keyword">procesos judiciales eficaces</span>, justos y sostenidos en un profundo conocimiento del derecho y la realidad social de nuestros clientes.</p>
                     </div>
                     
                     <div class="description-card">
                         <div class="card-header">
                             <div class="card-icon">
                                 <i class="fas fa-crosshairs"></i>
                             </div>
                             <h3>Propósito Claro</h3>
                         </div>
                         <p>Brindar a <span class="keyword">profesionales</span> la posibilidad de iniciar su vida laboral sin el peso de una deuda que <span class="keyword">limita sus oportunidades</span> y posterga sus proyectos. Sabemos que detrás de cada título hay años de <span class="keyword">esfuerzo, compromiso y sacrificio</span>.</p>
                     </div>
                     
                     <div class="description-card">
                         <div class="card-header">
                             <div class="card-icon">
                                 <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
                             </div>
                             <h3>Alcance Nacional</h3>
                         </div>
                         <p>Actuamos con <span class="keyword">alcance nacional</span>, acompañando causas en cada provincia con la misma <span class="keyword">dedicación, cercanía y compromiso</span>, sin importar la distancia. Gracias a un <span class="keyword">enfoque ágil y profesional</span>, logramos que cada persona pueda acceder a una <span class="keyword">defensa legal de calidad</span>.</p>
                     </div>
                     
                     <div class="description-card">
                         <div class="card-header">
                             <div class="card-icon">
                                 <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                             </div>
                             <h3>Estrategia Integral</h3>
                         </div>
                         <p>Combinamos <span class="keyword">experiencia legal</span>, <span class="keyword">atención personalizada</span> y una <span class="keyword">estrategia orientada a resultados</span>. Cada caso que representamos es una oportunidad para <span class="keyword">transformar un obstáculo en un nuevo comienzo</span>.</p>
                     </div>
                     
                     <div class="description-card">
                         <div class="card-header">
                             <div class="card-icon">
                                 <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                             </div>
                             <h3>Nuestra Filosofía</h3>
                         </div>
                         <p>En nuestro estudio, creemos que <span class="keyword">estudiar no debe ser una condena económica</span>, sino una <span class="keyword">inversión en el futuro</span>. Acompañamos a quienes decidieron apostar por su educación para que también puedan apostar por su <span class="keyword">libertad</span>.</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
             </div>
         </section>
    </main>
    
    <Footer />
    <WhatsAppButton />
</Layout>

<style>
    .quienes-somos-page {
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5e5e5 0%, #d8d8d8 25%, #c9c9c9 50%, #bebebe 75%, #b5b5b5 100%);
        scroll-margin-top: 120px;
        position: relative;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .quienes-somos-page::before {
        content: '';
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: 
            radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.02) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(circle at 40% 60%, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.01) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
        animation: backgroundFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes backgroundFloat {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
        33% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(0.5deg); }
        66% { transform: translateY(5px) rotate(-0.5deg); }
    }

    .quienes-somos-section {
        padding: clamp(8rem, 20vh, 14rem) 0 2rem 0; /* Aumentado desde 6rem a 8rem */
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #393939 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        min-height: 50vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .quienes-somos-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: 
            radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
            radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .banner-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (min-width: 769px) {
        .banner-container {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            animation: bannerSlideIn 1.2s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
        }
    }

    @keyframes bannerSlideIn {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    .banner-illustration {
        flex: 0 0 300px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg);
    }

    @media (min-width: 769px) {
        .banner-illustration {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: scale(0.8) rotate(-10deg);
            animation: illustrationFloat 1.5s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
        }
    }

    @keyframes illustrationFloat {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg);
        }
    }

    .illustration-placeholder {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 50%;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 2px solid rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .illustration-placeholder::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: -50%;
        width: 200%;
        height: 200%;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
        transform: rotate(45deg);
        transition: all 0.6s ease;
        opacity: 0;
    }

    .illustration-placeholder:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
        animation: shimmer 1.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    .illustration-placeholder:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        border-color: rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.6);
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.3);
    }

    @keyframes shimmer {
        0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
        100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
    }

    .banner-content {
        flex: 1;
        color: white;
    }

    .banner-title {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        position: relative;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
    }

    @media (min-width: 769px) {
        .banner-title {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-30px);
            animation: titleSlideIn 1s ease-out 0.9s forwards;
        }
    }

    @keyframes titleSlideIn {
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    .banner-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 0;
        width: 100px;
        height: 5px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CA0101, #E30613);
        border-radius: 3px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 769px) {
        .banner-title::after {
            width: 0;
            animation: underlineExpand 1s ease-out 1.6s forwards;
        }
    }

    @keyframes underlineExpand {
        to {
            width: 100px;
        }
    }

    .banner-description h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.4;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #FFFBFB;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    }

    .banner-description p {
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.4rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #E0DCDC;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    /* Bottom strip like in the reference image */
    .quienes-somos-section::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 10px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CA0101, #E30613, #E0DCDC);
    }

    /* Sección de Misión y Visión */
    .mission-vision-section {
        padding: 4rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .mission-vision-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        color: #393939;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .mission-vision-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
        gap: 3rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

         .mission-card, .vision-card {
         background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
         padding: 3.5rem 2.5rem;
         border-radius: 24px;
         text-align: center;
         box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
         border: 1px solid rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.08);
         transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
         position: relative;
         overflow: hidden;
         backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
         opacity: 1;
         transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
     }

     @media (min-width: 769px) {
         .mission-card, .vision-card {
             opacity: 0;
             transform: translateY(50px) scale(0.9);
             animation: cardSlideIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
         }

         .mission-card {
             animation-delay: 0.2s;
         }

         .vision-card {
             animation-delay: 0.4s;
         }
     }

     @keyframes cardSlideIn {
         to {
             opacity: 1;
             transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
         }
     }

    .mission-card::before, .vision-card::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 4px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CA0101, #E30613);
        transform: scaleX(0);
        transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

    .mission-card:hover::before, .vision-card:hover::before {
        transform: scaleX(1);
    }

         .mission-card:hover, .vision-card:hover {
         transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
         box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
         border-color: rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.15);
     }

         .card-icon {
         font-size: 3.5rem;
         margin-bottom: 2rem;
         display: flex;
         align-items: center;
         justify-content: center;
         filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
     }
     
     .card-icon i {
         font-size: 3.5rem;
         color: #CA0101;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
     }
     
     .mission-card:hover .card-icon, .vision-card:hover .card-icon {
         transform: scale(1.1);
         filter: drop-shadow(0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15));
     }
     
     .mission-card h3, .vision-card h3 {
         color: #CA0101;
         font-size: 1.8rem;
         margin-bottom: 2rem;
         font-weight: 700;
         text-transform: uppercase;
         letter-spacing: 1.5px;
         position: relative;
     }
     
     .mission-card h3::after, .vision-card h3::after {
         content: '';
         position: absolute;
         bottom: -8px;
         left: 50%;
         transform: translateX(-50%);
         width: 40px;
         height: 3px;
         background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CA0101, #E30613);
         border-radius: 2px;
         opacity: 0;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
     }
     
     .mission-card:hover h3::after, .vision-card:hover h3::after {
         opacity: 1;
         width: 60px;
     }

    .mission-card p, .vision-card p {
        color: #393939;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-align: left;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .banner-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .banner-illustration {
            flex: none;
        }

        .banner-title::after {
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .quienes-somos-section {
            padding-top: clamp(10rem, 25vh, 16rem); /* Padding específico para móvil */
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .mission-vision-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
                 .mission-card, .vision-card {
             padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
         }
         
         .mission-card h3, .vision-card h3 {
             font-size: 1.4rem;
             margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
         }
         
         .mission-card p, .vision-card p {
             font-size: 1rem;
             line-height: 1.6;
         }
         
         .card-icon {
             font-size: 3rem;
             margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
             display: flex;
             align-items: center;
             justify-content: center;
         }
         
         .card-icon i {
             font-size: 3rem;
             color: #CA0101;
         }
     }
     
     /* Sección de Descripción Detallada */
     .detailed-description-section {
         padding: 6rem 0;
         background: linear-gradient(135deg, #393939 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
         color: white;
         position: relative;
         overflow: hidden;
     }
     
     .detailed-description-section::before {
         content: '';
         position: absolute;
         top: 0;
         left: 0;
         right: 0;
         bottom: 0;
         background: 
             radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
             radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(227, 6, 19, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
         pointer-events: none;
     }
     
     .section-title {
         text-align: center;
         font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
         color: #F5F5F5;
         margin-bottom: 4rem;
         font-weight: 700;
         position: relative;
         z-index: 2;
     }
     
     .section-title::after {
         content: '';
         position: absolute;
         bottom: -15px;
         left: 50%;
         transform: translateX(-50%);
         width: 80px;
         height: 4px;
         background: linear-gradient(90deg, #CA0101, #E30613);
         border-radius: 2px;
     }
     
     .description-cards-grid {
         display: grid;
         grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
         gap: 2rem;
         max-width: 1200px;
         margin: 0 auto;
         position: relative;
         z-index: 2;
     }
     
     .description-card {
         background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
         padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
         border-radius: 16px;
         border: 1px solid rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.2);
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
         position: relative;
         overflow: hidden;
         box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
         opacity: 1;
         transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
     }

     @media (min-width: 769px) {
         .description-card {
             opacity: 0;
             transform: translateY(50px) scale(0.9);
             animation: descriptionSlideIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
         }

         .description-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
         .description-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
         .description-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
         .description-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
         .description-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
     }

     @keyframes descriptionSlideIn {
         to {
             opacity: 1;
             transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
         }
     }
     
     .description-card::before {
         content: '';
         position: absolute;
         top: 0;
         left: 0;
         right: 0;
         height: 2px;
         background: #CA0101;
         opacity: 0.6;
     }
     
     .description-card:hover {
         transform: translateY(-4px);
         background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
         border-color: rgba(202, 1, 1, 0.3);
         box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
     }
     
     .card-header {
         display: flex;
         align-items: center;
         gap: 1rem;
         margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
     }
     
     .card-header .card-icon {
         font-size: 2.2rem;
         color: #CA0101;
         opacity: 0.8;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
         display: flex;
         align-items: center;
         justify-content: center;
         width: 50px;
         height: 50px;
     }
     
     .card-header .card-icon i {
         font-size: 2.2rem;
         color: #CA0101;
         transition: all 0.3s ease;
     }
     
     .description-card:hover .card-header .card-icon {
         opacity: 1;
     }
     
     .card-header h3 {
         color: #CA0101;
         font-size: 1.4rem;
         font-weight: 700;
         margin: 0;
         text-transform: uppercase;
         letter-spacing: 1px;
     }
     
     .description-card p {
         color: #E0DCDC;
         line-height: 1.7;
         margin: 0;
         font-size: 1rem;
         text-align: left;
         opacity: 0.95;
     }
     
     /* Estilos para palabras clave */
     .keyword {
         color: #CA0101;
         font-weight: 600;
         position: relative;
         padding: 0 1px;
     }
     
     @media (max-width: 768px) {
         .detailed-description-section {
             padding: 4rem 0;
         }
         
         .section-title {
             font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
             margin-bottom: 3rem;
         }
         
         .description-cards-grid {
             grid-template-columns: 1fr;
             gap: 2rem;
             padding: 0 1rem;
         }
         
         .description-card {
             padding: 1.5rem 1.2rem;
         }
         
         .card-header {
             flex-direction: column;
             text-align: center;
             gap: 0.8rem;
         }
         
         .card-header .card-icon {
             font-size: 2rem;
         }
         
         .card-header h3 {
             font-size: 1.2rem;
         }
         
         .description_card p {
             font-size: 0.95rem;
             line-height: 1.6;
         }
         
         .keyword {
             font-weight: 500;
         }
     }
 </style>
